RIPEMD-160 implementation — public domain
========================================

The files ripemd160.c / ripemd160.h in this directory are a standalone
RIPEMD-160 implementation written for this project directly from the public
RIPEMD-160 specification:

    H. Dobbertin, A. Bosselaers, B. Preneel,
    "RIPEMD-160: A Strengthened Version of RIPEMD" (1996).

This implementation is released into the public domain. You may use, copy,
modify, and distribute it for any purpose, with or without attribution, and
without warranty of any kind. It has been verified against the canonical
RIPEMD-160 test vectors.
